summary: A collection of Celtic themed paintings for use in user created plugins for Elder Scrolls V Skyrim
descriptionHtml:
Ever notice there are no paintings in Skyrim? This pack offers a collection of Celtic themed paintings for use in user created plugins for Elder Scrolls V Skyrim. Though the paintings are done, this is technically a WIPz, tapestries and rugs are planned for future updates. There are 105 paintings in this collection divided by type. This is a resource only, and may be used freely provided credit is given to me. May not be combined with other resource packs.

Like my work? Want to see what's next?
